<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFRikshospitalet_University_Hospital2006"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Rikshospitalet_University_Hospital&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Rikshospitalet University Hospital (page does not exist)">Rikshospitalet University Hospital</a> (April 2006). <a href="http://www.clinicaltrials.gov/ct/show/NCT00318825" class="external text" title="http://www.clinicaltrials.gov/ct/show/NCT00318825" rel="nofollow">"Clinical Trial: Nitrous Oxide for Analgesia During Colonoscopy"</a>. ClinicalTrials.gov<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.clinicaltrials.gov/ct/show/NCT00318825" class="external free" title="http://www.clinicaltrials.gov/ct/show/NCT00318825" rel="nofollow">http://www.clinicaltrials.gov/ct/show/NCT00318825</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Clinical+Trial%3A+Nitrous+Oxide+for+Analgesia+During+Colonoscopy&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Rikshospitalet+University+Hospital&amp;rft.au=Rikshospitalet+University+Hospital&amp;rft.date=April+2006&amp;rft.pub=ClinicalTrials.gov&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clinicaltrials.gov%2Fct%2Fshow%2FNCT00318825&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Colonoscopy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
